<table><tr><td> National Clinical Guideline Centre . Routine preoperative tests for elective surgery. London (UK): National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE); 2016 Apr 5. 16 p.&nbsp;(NICE guideline; no. 45).&nbsp;</td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180712205534/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=50177&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=https%253a%252f%252fwww.nice.org.uk%252fguidance%252fNG45">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712205534im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
