    <div id="status-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: National Collaborating Centre for Acute Care. Preoperative tests: the use of routine preoperative tests for elective surgery: evidence, methods &amp; guidance. London (UK): National Institute for Clinical Excellence (NICE); 2003 Jun. 108 p. [118 references]</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
    </div>
