, <a href="/web/20180712205534/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0016529&amp;fLockTerm=Forced+expiratory+volume+function">Forced expiratory volume function</a>
, <a href="/web/20180712205534/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0017654&amp;fLockTerm=Glomerular+Filtration+Rate">Glomerular Filtration Rate</a>
